metadata.description: The Provenonce Genesis Penthouse remits a digital key secured on the Ethereum blockchain. Unlike other projects, your ERC-721 DEED powered by the Provenonce Standard is more than conceptual equity. Ownership with us confers immediate access and enjoyment rights to the Genesis Penthouse. The Provenonce Standard is a chain agnostic meta protocol for the asset management of digital properties. Penthouse owners can lease their digital properties with our browser-based smart contract wallet.
metadata.name: Genesis Penthouse 001: NEW YORK - DAYTIME
